{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, He et al. (2015) introduced collaborative filtering and view-based explainable AI methods, enhancing users' transparency.",
    "This system has utilized user reviews and ratings to assess the attributes of a particular item and employed a ranking algorithm to generate tailored suggestions (He et al., 2015).",
    "Several other scholarly works have used similar techniques; however, some of the most significant have used augmented product recommendations (Cheng et al., 2019), reinforcement learningbased product recommendations (Wang, Chen, et al., 2018; Wang, He, et al., 2018), and collaborative filtering (Wang, Chen, et al., 2018; Wang, He, et al., 2018).",
    "The reinforcement learning-based approach also uses a policy-guided graph search technique and a soft rewards strategy (Xian et al., 2019).",
    "Collaborative filtering is a commonly employed method for personalized recommendations (Schafer et al., 2007), but it needs more comprehensibility."
  ]
}